# Cloud boot (core)

- Read `AGENTS.md` first; follow the verify command after plot-related changes.
- Keep `.cursor/environment.json` lean — install deps only; no Docker/`start` unless services exist.
- Use agent title prefixes from `AGENTS.md`: `[impl]`, `[review]`, `[chore]`, `[research]`, `[domain]`.
- One primary category and one clear outcome per run.
- Do not install heavy ML stacks (torch, transformers, etc.) into this environment; use a separate env/repo for that work.
